{"error":0,"message":"","data":[{"show_ID":"2005","airdate":"1513018800","name_switch":"off","DJ":"ziona and Slaygon","showname":"Achtung - MONDAY with Der Danko!","blurb":"Hi All SLAYfellaz,\n\nFirst time since ziona is doing shows, a Monday will replace a Tuesday evening occasionally, but you can expect the usual show with the special guest star Danko, who did lots, LOTS of SIDs and also he is a professional producer since the '90s. Nowadays he is a member of the Fairlight demogroup as well. \nSince he is an adopted brother of Slaygon, our beloved Leader will join to co-host the show too :)\n\nSLAY tuned with us and request your favourite songs! ","nice_showname":"<strong><big>ziona and Slaygon<\/big><\/strong><br \/>Achtung - MONDAY with Der Danko!","nice_airdate":"Monday 11th December, 2017<br \/>at 20:00 USRT"},{"show_ID":"2006","airdate":"1513191600","name_switch":"off","DJ":"Bozzy and the Bint","showname":"BBKB","blurb":"It's the Taint of the Show\u2122 again, so it's time for Boz to utter complete bollocks in between your requests. Thankfully, Kate is here to translate some of it into English. All aboard the Train-Wreck, WOO WOOH!","nice_showname":"<strong><big>Bozzy and the Bint<\/big><\/strong><br \/>BBKB","nice_airdate":"Wednesday 13th December, 2017<br \/>at 20:00 USRT"},{"show_ID":"1992","airdate":"1513515600","name_switch":"off","DJ":"IImmortal vs PhasedBased","showname":"Sunday Detox","blurb":"Hi all,\nIt has been a few years and it took some work and determination to get back again. But with some serious help from PhasedBased we are finally back. I would like to invite you to join us for a lazy Sunday afternoon, feeling the hangover just slip away while we listen to some easy going tunes.","nice_showname":"<strong><big>IImmortal vs PhasedBased<\/big><\/strong><br \/>Sunday Detox","nice_airdate":"Sunday 17th December, 2017<br \/>at 14:00 USRT"}]}